data.title: CHARM redirect
data.text:
You have been redirected to the new CHARM website at www.charm.kcl.ac.uk.

This new site provides integrated access to CHARM's online discography (July 2009), downloadable recordings (July 2009), analytical software and training materials, and a variety of resources relating to the history of recording.
